{"tid":1706264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夠啦， 今日真係夠啦。。。","createTime":"2019-11-11T04:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T05:32:15.000Z","uid":245673,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"400f78c0d88df231802b40507abd7aa9e42a67fa","tid":1706264,"uid":245673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:53:51.000Z","msg":"今日好正， 今朝搭地鐵去到調景嶺，見到有幾度都口角緊， 我緊係幫拖， 我發覺身邊好多人一齊幫口， 感覺身邊都有好多同路人， 幾個廢老藍絲寸到唔敢出聲， 其中有一個堅。裝修佬仲話乜撚野個靚仔比鎗打係神安排， 在場既人包括我即刻屌佢老母<br />\n<br />\n特別有兩個絲打係咁屌佢同講道理， 我真係比佢地迷到講堅， 雖然我有女朋友<br />\n<br />\n係要朝早先可以connect到人， 夜晚放工個個返屋企， 得少數人出黎<br />\n<br />\n朝早反而可以攬炒啲廢老<br />\n<br />\n同埋最緊要，唔少得周圍行街既兄弟， 今日已經完成quota, 好多人返唔到，好多店關左<br />\n<br />\n以後記住朝早先好搞， 今日目的已達講堅<br />\n<br />\n天佑慈幼手足。。。"},{"pid":"aa2ee430d92c48e5f1a3f449599586828f498377","tid":1706264,"uid":121182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:55:53.000Z","msg":"呢啲絲打係正野黎"},{"pid":"dcb620e4cba78945e1e79a7ee4ec1bd95cf35272","tid":1706264,"uid":124711,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:56:36.000Z","msg":"我全公司今日都返唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次 真係無唸過會成功"},{"pid":"f722c44d3cc9509ba98defa7a49b91359ff223bc","tid":1706264,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:57:35.000Z","msg":"Keep住"},{"pid":"40d806a1498900f13e695c94889ab750e87e62fb","tid":1706264,"uid":245673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:03:18.000Z","msg":"今日罷工黎講真係算成功<br />\n<br />\n今日個位擋門既絲打鬧個裝修佬同擋門真係好型， 我當然都有幫手鬧<br />\n<br />\n另外， 再次再次感激行街手足， 冇你地， 今日唔會咁成功<br />\n<br />\n天佑慈幼義士"},{"pid":"3a8da87d7a0af03530d42f6b3e25b229a22bb059","tid":1706264,"uid":67813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:05:26.000Z","msg":"人地拎條命出黎"},{"pid":"d0576be05ecbe47c2e14171f8634a3efbdae7bb5","tid":1706264,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:07:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">周街防暴，狗屋有機會唔夠人，結界巨量火魔</span></span>"},{"pid":"50c7687966b77124018d90f027981a9d5f2e2007","tid":1706264,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:14:18.000Z","msg":"我夠你老母<br />\n大把人放工打下場"},{"pid":"a06e4436a92c886942ff3f824e164f33cdbf6e7a","tid":1706264,"uid":245673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:26:26.000Z","msg":"我意思係想手足休息夠， 以後轉朝早搞<br />\n<br />\n一來回響更大， 啲狗辛苦兩陪朝早搞"},{"pid":"33ecd0397394be88a75d67422ce558b859f9cc06","tid":1706264,"uid":154505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50c7687966b77124018d90f027981a9d5f2e2007","tid":1706264,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:14:18.000Z","msg":"我夠你老母<br />\n大把人放工打下場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:32:15.000Z","msg":"聽朝再黎"}]}